This directory contains some tests of flx2tab.

1. simplest case of a single spectrum

% flx2tab input1.txt Test1 test1.fits

2. Case of five spectra which have been calculated using
   a model with a single parameter (alpha). When used in xspec the table
   model will include a redshift parameter.

% flx2tab input2.txt Test2 test2.fits nspec=5 parinfofile=parinput2.txt redshift=yes

3. As case 2 except that the input data are in micron and ergs/cm^2/s/um.

% flx2tab input2.txt Test3 test3.fits nspec=5 parinfofile=parinput2.txt redshift=yes xunit=micron yunit=ergs/cm^2/s/um

4. Case of a single spectrum but energies in reverse order

% flx2tab input4.txt Test4 test4.fits



